      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/260303-symposiwm/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h4 id=&#34;croeso-ir-stori-wyllt-symposiwmwelcome-to-the-stori-wyllt-symposium&#34;&gt;Croeso i&amp;rsquo;r Stori Wyllt symposiwm!&lt;br&gt;Welcome to the Stori Wyllt symposium!&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The Stori Wyllt Symposiwm was an ideal opportunity for the teachers, naturalists and creatives from the four schools to meet each other in-person and share ideas at a central location in Ceredigion (Moody Meadows at Bargoed Farm ar bwys Llwyncelyn).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The Stori Wyllt schools are, from the south to the north, Ysgol Gynradd Aberteifi, Ysgol Llanarth, Ysgol Gynradd Aberaeron and Ysgol Llanilar.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
